Uses of Class
nodebasis.Message

  • Packages that use Message 
    Package Description
    nodebasis  

    • Uses of Message in nodebasis

      Subclasses of Message in nodebasis 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AgentMessage
      The AgentMessage class extends the Message class, and is defined by the sole purpose of spreading knowledge regarding the directions to various events which has occurred within the node network.

      It is important to note that whenever a node receives an instance to this class, that the node foremost fetches data from the message before proceeding with updating the message itself.
      class  RequestMessage
      The RequestMessage class extends the Message class, and is defined by the sole purpose of fetching information regarding a specific event, on the request of a node.
